{"title":"Kehapesu","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"oak-shower-gel-imperial-for-men","title":"Magrada Oak Shower Gel For Men 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYour healthy, clean, moisturized skin! The sulphate-free shower gel is designed specifically for men and contains aloe, which moistens and calms the skin, and the powerful oak root extract, which pampers and caresses irritated skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eDandelion extract\u003c\/span\u003e has anti-inflammatory and anti-irritation effect on the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Body\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAloe extract \u003c\/span\u003epromotes wound healing, moisturizes, refreshes, is anti-inflammatory, soothes, softens irritation and protects the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOak root extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas natural antimicrobial properties, soothing irritated and swollen skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe fragrance is derived from the blossoms of the evergreen shrub \u003cem\u003eOsmanthus\u003c\/em\u003e, the aroma is fresh and exquisite. The bush is also known as devilwood, because its smell is nothing less than tempting. Soft, woody, sensual, milky and leathery notes emerge from the fragrance notes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eApply the shower gel on damp skin with light circular movements. Rinse and dry.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Chloride, Citric Acid, Taraxacum Officinale (Dandelion) Extract, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract, Quercus Robur (Oak) Root Extract, Argan Oil Glycereth-8 Esters, Isostearamide MIPA, Panthenol, Parfum, Glyceryl Laurate, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 91,64%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927700713799,"sku":"","price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-oak-shower-gel-for-men-250ml-478014.png?v=1739897400"},{"product_id":"copy-of-organic-body-wash-250ml-1","title":"Vielö Organic Body Wash 250ml","description":"\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNourishing organic body wash, specially designed to cleanse, nourish and moisturise dry and sensitive skin gently.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), wheat protein (moisturising), soy protein (strengthening) and organic extracts of arnica (soothing), birch leaf (purifying) and rosemary (stimulating).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to wet skin. Leave on briefly. Rinse thoroughly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cu\u003e:\u003c\/u\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Aqua*, Glycerin**, Decyl Glucoside*, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Xanthan Gum*, Betaine*, Polyglyceryl-3 Caprate*, Citric Acid*, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein*, Hydrolyzed Wheat Gluten*, Citronellol**\/***, Hydrolyzed Soy Protein*, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Arnica Montana Flower Extract**, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Caesalpinia Spinosa Gum*, Betula Alba Leaf Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (68,3%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49091841130823,"sku":null,"price":27.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-body-wash-250ml-637632.jpg?v=1739897340"},{"product_id":"cosmos-organic-certified-extra-gentle-shower-gel-fruity-wild-strawberry-250ml","title":"Cosmos Organic Certified Extra Gentle Shower Gel - Fruity Wild Strawberry 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eExtra gentle and certified \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eorganic natural shower gel with a delicious and fruity 100% natural wild strawberry scent. Enriched with natural glycerin, it gently cleanses and moisturizes the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eIts exemplary formula is respectful of your skin and the environment: without sulfates, parabens, PEG, phenoxyethanol or cocamidopropyl betaine. Its creamy texture, delicate foam and fresh lemon verbana scent create a real moment of relaxation in your shower.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eThe shower gel is suitable for all skin types and will be appreciated by the whole family. Children under 3 years old are not recommended to use this shower gel.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Wild strawberry shower gel can be used daily on the face and body. Apply the shower gel on the body, avoid the eye area. Rinse and dry. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua (water), hordeum stem water*, lauryl glucoside, sodium cocoyl glutamate, glycerin, coco glucoside, citric acid, glyceryl oleate, parfum (fragrance), sodium benzoate, potassium sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* Ingredient from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e** Processed from ingredients from Organic Farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eMade in France.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIngredients 99.5% natural and 10.5% from organic farming\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAll raw materials processed in France\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eShower gel made in France (Alsace)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNo controversial ingredients , 100% good for your skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWithout palm oil or derivatives\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not release pollutants into water\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePackaging: 100% recycled and recyclable bottle made in Europe\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"FUN!ETHIC","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49111920607559,"sku":"","price":6.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/cosmos-organic-certified-extra-gentle-shower-gel-fruity-wild-strawberry-250ml-376157.png?v=1739897340"},{"product_id":"cosmos-organic-certified-extra-gentle-shower-gel-discreet-saline-scent-250ml","title":"Cosmos Organic Certified Extra Gentle Shower Gel - Discreet Saline Scent 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eExtra gentle and certified \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eorganic natural shower gel with a discreet marine and saline scent. Enriched with natural glycerin, it gently cleanses and moisturizes the skin.  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eIts exemplary formula is respectful of your skin and the environment: without sulfates, parabens, PEG, phenoxyethanol or cocamidopropyl betaine. Its creamy texture, delicate foam and fresh lemon verbana scent create a real moment of relaxation in your shower.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eThe shower gel is suitable for all skin types and will be appreciated by the whole family. Children under 3 years old are not recommended to use this shower gel.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Marine shower gel can be used daily on the face and body. Apply the shower gel on the body, avoid the eye area. Rinse and dry.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua (water), hordeum stem water*, lauryl glucoside, sodium cocoyl glutamate, glycerin, coco glucoside, citric acid, glyceryl oleate, parfum (fragrance), benzyl salicylate, geraniol, sodium benzoate, potassium sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* Ingredient from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e** Processed from ingredients from Organic Farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eMade in France.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIngredients 99.5% natural and 10.5% from organic farming\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAll raw materials processed in France\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eShower gel made in France (Alsace)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNo controversial ingredients, 100% good for your skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWithout palm oil or derivatives\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not release pollutants into water\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePackaging:  100% recycled and recyclable bottle made in Europe \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"FUN!ETHIC","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49111947116871,"sku":null,"price":6.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/cosmos-organic-certified-extra-gentle-shower-gel-discreet-saline-scent-250ml-846314.png?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"cosmos-organic-certified-extra-gentle-shower-gel-refreshing-tonic-scent-250ml","title":"Cosmos Organic Certified Extra Gentle Shower Gel - Refreshing Tonic Scent 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eExtra gentle and certified \u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eorganic natural shower gel with an invigorating and refreshing 100% natural lemon verbena scent. Enriched with natural glycerin, it gently cleanses and moisturizes the skin.  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eIts exemplary formula is respectful of your skin and the environment: without sulfates, parabens, PEG, phenoxyethanol or cocamidopropyl betaine. Its creamy texture, delicate foam and fresh lemon verbana scent create a real moment of relaxation in your shower. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eThe shower gel is suitable for all skin types and will be appreciated by the whole family. Children under 3 years old are not recommended to use this shower gel.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lemon verbena shower gel can be used daily on the face and body. Apply the shower gel on the body, avoid the eye area. Rinse and dry. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua (water), hordeum stem water*, lauryl glucoside, sodium cocoyl glutamate, glycerin, coco glucoside, citric acid, glyceryl oleate, parfum (fragrance), citral, limonene, sodium benzoate, potassium sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* Ingredient from Organic Farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e** Processed from ingredients from Organic Farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eMade in France.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIngredients 99.5% natural and 10.5% from organic farming\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAll raw materials processed in France\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eShower gel made in France (Alsace)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNo controversial ingredients, 100% good for your skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWithout palm oil or derivatives\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not release pollutants into water\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePackaging: 100% recycled and recyclable bottles made in Europe\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"FUN!ETHIC","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49112004165959,"sku":null,"price":6.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/cosmos-organic-certified-extra-gentle-shower-gel-refreshing-tonic-scent-250ml-391460.png?v=1739897343"},{"product_id":"bee-it-regenerating-shower-gel-250ml","title":"BEE IT Regenerating Shower Gel 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSensory body wash with naturally active biological ingredients with a regenerating action.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003ePromotes the natural feeling of well-being thanks to the beneficial properties of propolis and organic honey.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eApply all over the body. Rinse off, appreciating your moment.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eAqua [Water], Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Parfum [Fragrance], Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Potassium sorbate, Sodium benzoate, Citric acid, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Coumarin, Limonene, Alpha-isomethyl ionone, Hydroxycitronellal, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel\/Honey*, Propolis wax.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e100% Natural Ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49354419503431,"sku":"","price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-regenerating-shower-gel-250ml-523322.jpg?v=1739897335"},{"product_id":"bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-blue-for-kids-250ml","title":"BEE IT Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash Blue for Kids 250ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003ePhysiological pH shampoo \u0026amp; body wash rich in natural ingredients to enjoy the bath time as a pleasant experience of play and creativity. With organic aloe vera, sweet almond oil, organic honey and propolis, for a delicate and nourishing action.\u003cbr\u003eAmused and clean, his hair will be velvety and luminous, and his skin will be even softer and more fragrant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to hair and body and massage gently, then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Coco-glucoside, Glyceryl oleate, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Glycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Parfum, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate, Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Myristyl lactate, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Citric acid, Calendula officinalis extract, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel*, Propolis, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNatural product with physiological pH 4.5-5.5\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49354588979527,"sku":null,"price":12.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-blue-for-kids-250ml-687213.png?v=1739897342"},{"product_id":"bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-pink-for-kids-250ml","title":"BEE IT Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash Pink for Kids 250ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003ePhysiological pH shampoo \u0026amp; body wash rich in natural ingredients to enjoy the bath time as a pleasant experience of play and creativity. With organic aloe vera, sweet almond oil, organic honey and propolis, for a delicate and nourishing action.\u003cbr\u003eAmused and clean, his hair will be velvety and luminous, and his skin will be even softer and more fragrant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to hair and body and massage gently, then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Coco-glucoside, Glyceryl oleate, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Glycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Parfum, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate, Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Myristyl lactate, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Citric acid, Calendula officinalis extract, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel*, Propolis, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNatural product with physiological pH 4.5-5.5\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49354641178951,"sku":null,"price":12.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-pink-for-kids-250ml-813819.png?v=1739897342"},{"product_id":"naif-cleansing-wash-gel-200ml","title":"NAIF Cleansing Wash Gel 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNaïf cleansing wash gel for baby \u0026amp; kids cleanses the skin mildly and prevents dry skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eWashing gel for bath and shower\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eCleanses and cares for the sensitive baby skin with natural oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e0% SLES\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eWithout microplastics and mineral oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply a small amount to the baby's skin. Rinse off and dry. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Aqua\/Water, Coco-Glucoside (\u003ci\u003ecloudy liquid derived from coconut\u003c\/i\u003e), Sodium Coco-Sulfate (\u003ci\u003emade from the fatty acids of coconut oil\u003c\/i\u003e), Cocamidopropyl Betaine (\u003ci\u003enaturally-derived surfactant that is sourced from coconut oil\u003c\/i\u003e), Glycerin, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Gossypium Hirsutum (Cotton Seed) Extract, Glyceryl Oleate, Tocopherol, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides Citrate, Sodium Levulinate, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Chloride, Fragrance (allergen-free), Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446208602439,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-cleansing-wash-gel-200ml-254915.png?v=1739897263"},{"product_id":"magrada-bubble-shower-gel-400ml","title":"Magrada Luxurious Bubble Shower Gel 400ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn collaboration with The Bubble Gallery, Magrada has created a luxurious and enchanting product line that combines the lavish aromas of the finest quality sparkling wine and delicate botanical extracts to offer you a truly enjoyable experience. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBUBBLE shower gel takes you on a luxurious relaxation journey, indulging you with the exclusive scent and a rich shower experience.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply on skin with light circular movements, rinse with water.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Aqua, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Chloride, Citric Acid, Parfum, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract, Isostearamide MIPA, Panthenol, Glycerin, Glyceryl Laurate, Juniperus Communis (Juniper) Fruit Extract, Acacia Concinna (Shikakai) Fruit Extract, Balanites Aegyptiaca (Soapberry Tree) Fruit Extract, Gypsophila Paniculata (White Saponaria) Root Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Sorbic Acid\\n \\nIngredients of natural origin: 93,97% \"}' data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":13057,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"15\":\"Calibri\",\"16\":12}'\u003eAqua, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Chloride, Citric Acid, Parfum, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract, Isostearamide MIPA, Panthenol, Glycerin, Glyceryl Laurate, Juniperus Communis (Juniper) Fruit Extract, Acacia Concinna (Shikakai) Fruit Extract, Balanites Aegyptiaca (Soapberry Tree) Fruit Extract, Gypsophila Paniculata (White Saponaria) Root Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Sorbic Acid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 93,97%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e vegan \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e EU allergen-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49583803728199,"sku":null,"price":25.8,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-luxurious-bubble-shower-gel-400ml-376033.png?v=1739897240"},{"product_id":"magrada-luxurious-bubble-hand-soap-400ml","title":"Magrada Luxurious Bubble Hand Soap 400ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIn partnership with Mulligalerii, Magrada has developed a truly luxurious and enchanting product series that combines the opulent aromas of top-quality sparkling wine with gentle botanical extracts to deliver an enjoyable experience. Gypsum flower, aloe, wash acacia, and desert date form a nurturing quartet that provides rich care for your skin. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis exclusive hand soap caresses your senses while the silky soap foam cleanses and moisturizes your skin, leaving it soft and radiant. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply on hands, rinse with water.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\" data-sheets-value='{\"1\":2,\"2\":\"Aqua, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Citric Acid, Sodium Chloride, Parfum, Isostearamide MIPA, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract, Sodium Lactate, Sodium PCA, Glyceryl Laurate, Acacia Concinna (Shikakai) Fruit Extract, Balanites Aegyptiaca (Soapberry Tree) Fruit Extract, Gypsophila Paniculata (White Saponaria) Root Extract, Glycine, Fructose, Urea, Niacinamide, Inositol, Lactic Acid, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Sorbic Acid\\n \\nIngredients of natural origin: 95,33%\"}' data-sheets-userformat='{\"2\":13057,\"3\":{\"1\":0},\"11\":4,\"12\":0,\"15\":\"Calibri\",\"16\":12}'\u003eAqua, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Citric Acid, Sodium Chloride, Parfum, Isostearamide MIPA, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract, Sodium Lactate, Sodium PCA, Glyceryl Laurate, Acacia Concinna (Shikakai) Fruit Extract, Balanites Aegyptiaca (Soapberry Tree) Fruit Extract, Gypsophila Paniculata (White Saponaria) Root Extract, Glycine, Fructose, Urea, Niacinamide, Inositol, Lactic Acid, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Sorbic Acid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 95,33%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e vegan \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e EU allergen-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49583815131463,"sku":null,"price":25.8,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-luxurious-bubble-hand-soap-400ml-861222.png?v=1739897260"},{"product_id":"nurme-soothing-body-wash-with-lavender-and-sage-essential-oils-250ml","title":"NURME Soothing Body Wash with Lavender and Sage Essential Oils 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eAwaken and nourish your skin daily with this naturally cleansing shower gel. Infused with the fragrant and therapeutic essential oils of Lavender and Clary Sage, you can start your day feeling clean and revitalised.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply on skin and rub, then rinse with water.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Sodium Coco-Sulfate*, Coco-Glucoside*, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein*, Glyceryl Oleate*, Sodium Benzoate*, Potassium Sorbate*, Citric Acid, Sodium Chloride, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil, Salvia Sclarea Oil, Linalool**, Geraniol**, Limonene**.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e* Natural cosmetics approved ingredient\u003cbr\u003e** Occurs naturally in essential oils\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915938468167,"sku":null,"price":8.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-soothing-body-wash-with-lavender-and-sage-essential-oils-250ml-409717.webp?v=1739897190"},{"product_id":"nurme-earthy-spices-warming-body-wash-250ml","title":"NURME Earthy Spices Warming Body Wash 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAwaken and nourish your skin daily with this naturally cleansing shower gel. Infused with the fragrant and therapeutic essential oils of Coriander and Black pepper, you can start your day feeling clean and revitalised.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply on skin and rub gently, then rinse with water.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Coco-Glucoside*, Sodium Coco-Sulfate*, Glyceryl Oleate*, Citric Acid, Sodium Chloride, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein*, Piper Nigrum Fruit Oil, Coriandrum Sativum Oil, Sodium Benzoate*, Potassium Sorbate*, Linalool**, Geraniol**, Limonene**.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e*Natural cosmetics approved ingredient\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e** Occurs naturally in essential oils\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915944694087,"sku":null,"price":8.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-earthy-spices-warming-body-wash-250ml-209851.webp?v=1739897169"},{"product_id":"nurme-mild-baby-shampoo-body-wash-200ml","title":"NURME Mild Baby Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThe Baby Shampoo \u0026amp; Shower Gel is a gentle cleanser that is particularly suitable for sensitive skin and can be used to wash the baby from their very first bath. The shampoo\/shower gel contains natural wheat protein and moisturizes the skin even during dry winter months. Organic and plant-based ingredients work like magic, nourishing the skin and cleansing the child from head to tiny toes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBaby skin is soft and delicate. It is more sensitive than adult skin and can easily become dry, painful, and flaky.\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eIt is essential to use specially formulated products for infants to protect their delicate skin from damage.\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eNurme Baby Range products, including the Baby Shampoo \u0026amp; Shower Gel, help care for a baby’s delicate skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOf course, this cleansing product can also be used by all other family members, especially those with sensitive skin!\u003cspan\u003e Nurme Baby Shampoo \u0026amp; Shower Gel, with its pure composition, is very gentle on the skin while being effective.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a small amount of shampoo\/shower gel to a washcloth or palm and gently massage the baby’s head and body. Rinse with water afterward. If the product gets into the eyes, rinse thoroughly with water.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua*, Coco-Glucoside*, Sodium Coco-Sulfate*, Coco-Glucoside (and) Glyceryl Oleate*, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein*, Sodium Benzoate (and) Potassium Sorbate*, Citric Acid*, Sodium Chloride*. \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Natural cosmetics approved ingredient, organic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915990241607,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-mild-baby-shampoo-body-wash-200ml-327281.webp?v=1739897183"},{"product_id":"madara-wild-woods-moisture-wash-500ml","title":"MÁDARA Wild Woods Moisture Wash 500ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eInfused with aromatic extracts of horsetail and absinthium, this heavenly scented moisture wash pays homage to Northern flora, capturing the freshness of wild woods.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe dermatologically tested formula has been crafted with natural physio-moisturisers, gently cleansing and hydrating the skin to leave it soft and supple. Formulated without harsh surfactants, synthetic fragrances and artificial colourants, it is suitable for both hands and body.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage and lather over damp skin, rinse well. Follow with MÁDARA hand or body cream of choice. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Sodium Coco-sulfate, Sodium cocoamphoacetate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Coco-glucoside, Citric acid, Aroma, Sodium PCA, Benzyl Alcohol, Aqua, Artemisia Absinthium (Absinthium) Herb Extract, Equisetum Arvense (Horsetail) Extract, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Limonene, Linalool, Eugenol, Citral\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916960665927,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-wild-woods-moisture-wash-500ml-660570.jpg?v=1739897158"},{"product_id":"madara-bitter-honey-moisture-wash-500ml","title":"MÁDARA Bitter Honey Moisture Wash 500ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eLather up and bathe in this heavenly scented body wash that captures the fragrant characteristics of dewy morning freshness, blooming meadowsweet and beautiful Northern summers.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThoughtfully crafted with natural physio-moisturisers, the caring formula nourishes as it cleanses, leaving behind soft, supple skin and an enticing scent.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFor use as a daily hand and body wash, it is dermatologically tested and free from harsh surfactants, synthetic fragrances and artificial colourants.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage and lather over damp skin, rinse well. Follow with MÁDARA hand or body cream of choice.  \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Sodium Coco-sulfate, Sodium cocoamphoacetate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Citric acid, Coco-glucoside, Aroma, Benzyl Alcohol, Aqua, Sodium PCA, Sodium Benzoate, Spiraea Ulmaria (Meadowsweet) Flower Extract, Galium Verum (Lady's Bedstraw\/Madara) Extract, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Chloride, Linalool, Limonene, Citrus Aurantium Peel Oil, Juniperus Virginiana Oil, Benzyl Salicylate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCOSMOS ORGANIC certified\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50916993106247,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-bitter-honey-moisture-wash-500ml-849581.jpg?v=1739897182"},{"product_id":"clarification-moisturizing-body-wash-powder-40g","title":"Clarification Moisturizing Body Wash Powder 40g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis brand believes in a future where beauty coexists harmoniously with sustainability.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% purity treatments, 0% added water!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Body Wash Powder with organic oats and white clay is very innovative. It foams instantly and generously on contact with water like a traditional shower gel. It is composed exclusively of gentle and natural origin ingredients and suits sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt is the natural cleansing treatment for the body that gently moisturizes and cleanses all skin types. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe plastic-free packaging made from recycled aluminum is compact and light, easy to transport. And of course n\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eo sulfates, no preservatives.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e Pour the equivalent of a teaspoon of powder into your hand, add some drops of water and rub hands together until it foams, then apply on wet skin. Repeat if necessary. Do not inhale or breathe the dust, avoid contact with eyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eSodium Lauroyl Glutamate, Aqua \/ Water, Kaolin, Avena Sativa Kernel Flour \/ Avena Sativa (Oat) Kernel Flour*, Sodium Myristoyl Glutamate, Citric Acid, Parfum \/ Fragrance, Glucose, Sodium Hyaluronate\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% of natural origin ingredients  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10% of the total ingredients come from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Clarification","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50964894712135,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/clarification-moisturizing-body-wash-powder-40g-139163.jpg?v=1739897166"},{"product_id":"clarification-duo-set-of-cleansing-powders-body-and-hair","title":"Clarification Duo Set of Cleansing Powders - Body and Hair","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis brand believes in a future where beauty coexists harmoniously with sustainability.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% purity treatments, 0% added water!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe set includes The Moisturizing Powder Shampoo (40g) and The Body Wash Powder (40g), both offer a unique care experience.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMoisturizing Powder Shampoo\u003c\/strong\u003e with organic rice and corn powder is an innovative washing powder for hair. It foams instantly and generously on contact with water like a classic shampoo. It is composed exclusively of gentle and natural origin ingredients and suits also sensitive scalps.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePowder Shampoo 100% natural origin ingredients provide hydration, volume and shine to the hair.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Body Wash Powder\u003c\/strong\u003e with organic oats and white clay is very innovative. It foams instantly and generously on contact with water like a traditional shower gel. It is composed exclusively of gentle and natural origin ingredients and suits sensitive skin.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eIt is the natural cleansing treatment for the body that gently moisturizes and cleanses all skin types. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMoisturizing Powder Shampoo: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003ePour the equivalent of a teaspoon of powder into your hand, apply to already wet hair. Repeat if necessary for longer hair. Do not inhale or breathe the dust, avoid contact with eyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Body Wash Powder: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003ePour the equivalent of a teaspoon of powder into your hand, add some drops of water and rub hands together until it foams, then apply on wet skin. Repeat if necessary.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eDo not inhale or breathe the dust, avoid contact with eyes. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMoisturizing Powder Shampoo: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSodium Myristoyl Glutamate, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Citric acid, Sodium chloride, Oryza Sativa St arch \/ Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch*, Zea Mays starch \/ Zea Mays (Corn) Starch*, Maltodextrin, aqua\/water, Kaolin, Sodium cocoate, Glucose, Parfum \/ Fragrance, Sodium Cocoyl Alaninate, Sodium Hyaluronate. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% of natural origin ingredients  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e11,12% of the total ingredients come from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Body Wash Powder: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSodium Lauroyl Glutamate, Aqua \/ Water, Kaolin, Avena Sativa Kernel Flour \/ Avena Sativa (Oat) Kernel Flour*, Sodium Myristoyl Glutamate, Citric Acid, Parfum \/ Fragrance, Glucose, Sodium Hyaluronate\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% of natural origin ingredients  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10% of the total ingredients come from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Clarification","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50965083717959,"sku":null,"price":34.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/clarification-duo-set-of-cleansing-powders-body-and-hair-537546.webp?v=1739897187"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-energizing-shower-gel-250ml","title":"LUUV Natural Energizing Carrot Shower Gel 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eImagine stepping into your shower and being greeted by a burst of citrusy goodness that awakens your senses and puts a smile on your face every morning. That’s exactly what this shower gel delivers with its pleasant citrus scent that’s bound to become your new favorite. But it’s more than just a fragrant delight. This shower gel is formulated to effectively remove dirt and grime, leaving your skin squeaky clean and revitalized. It also deeply moisturizes your skin, ensuring that you step out of the shower feeling as soft and smooth as a carrot straight from the garden.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe key ingredient is pure carrot oil, a rich source of essential vitamins that work wonders for your skin. It enhances skin elasticity, helping you maintain that youthful glow you’ve always wanted. Make it an essential part of your well-scented bathroom routine, and let the rejuvenating power of carrots and citrus awaken your senses and delight you every single day. Showering has never been this enjoyable!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMoisturizing\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eImproves skin elasticity\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRefreshing citrus scent\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eFor all skin types\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCoco-Glucoside\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis a detergent, 100% natural (derived from coconut), environmentally friendly and certified. The detergent is gentle – also suitable for sensitive skin and children.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCarrot oil\u003c\/span\u003e (specifically carrot seed oil) contains a lot of carotene, which gives a complexion-enhancing effect. Carrot oil is always in a carrier oil (i.e., diluted) because it is too intense on its own. It contains a lot of vitamin A. The natural SPF of carrot oil is around 40, but since it is diluted, it ends up around SPF 10.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shower gel on damp skin with light circular movements, rinse and dry.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Sodium Lauryl Glucose Carboxylate (and) Lauryl Glucoside, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Cocamidoprpyl Betaine, Glycerin, Betaine, Prunus Domestica (Plum) Seed oil, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Sodium Benzoate (and) Potassium Sorbate, Coco-Glucoside (and) Glyceryl Oleate, Cymbopogon Martini (Palmarosa) oil, Citric Acid, Parfum\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110691897671,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-energizing-carrot-shower-gel-250ml-522072.png?v=1740560025"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-exfoliating-shower-gel-250ml","title":"LUUV Natural Exfoliating Shower Gel 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNatural Exfoliating Shower Gel – the ultimate way to rejuvenate your skin and start your day with a refreshing burst of energy. This invigorating shower gel offers a dual-action formula that gently exfoliates and cleanses, leaving your skin irresistibly fresh and radiant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDesigned with your skin’s well-being in mind, our formula ensures a gentle exfoliation that sweeps away dead skin cells without causing any micro damage. Feel confident knowing that bamboo particles are not only kind to your skin but also eco-friendly, embracing the values of both beauty and sustainability. As the bamboo particles delicately scrub away impurities, they also awaken your skin’s natural renewal process, fostering improved elasticity and texture. Experience the joy of skin that feels irresistibly soft and smooth to the touch, every single day. The light and fresh scent of green tea not only invigorates your senses but also sets the stage for a perfect start to your day.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis exfoliating shower gel isn’t just a treat for the ladies – it’s versatile design caters to the dynamic lifestyles of both genders, making it an ideal addition to any daily routine. Welcome each day with skin that’s fresh, vibrant, and ready to take on the world.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGentle, but effective\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eDoesn\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e‘\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003et dry skin\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor daily use\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFresh green tea scent\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eSafe for the environment\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCoco-Glucoside\u003c\/span\u003e is a detergent, 100% natural (derived from coconut), environmentally friendly and certified. The detergent is gentle – also suitable for sensitive skin and children.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shower gel on damp skin with light circular movements, rinse and dry.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Bambusa Vulgaris powder, Vegetable Glycerin, Citric Acid, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Parfum\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110715982151,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-exfoliating-shower-gel-250ml-332480.png?v=1740725717"},{"product_id":"luuv-natural-kids-shower-foam-150ml","title":"LUUV Natural Kids Shower Foam 150ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis is LUUV kids shower foam – the ultimate bath-time companion that brings joy, playfulness, and eco-consciousness to your little one’s daily routine! Certified with the leading ECOCERT \/ COSMOS eco-certificate, this delightful foam will make showering an adventure filled with laughter and fun.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe understand that your child’s delicate skin deserves only the best, which is why this shower foam is crafted from carefully selected detergents that are gentle and won’t irritate your child’s precious skin. The sweet and juicy pear aroma is completely derived from natural sources, ensuring a captivating scent without any allergens. As for the vibrant pinkish purple color, a surprising secret ingredient is used – potato extract! That’s right, this eco-certified formula uses this natural wonder to create a mesmerizing hue that will captivate your child’s imagination. It’s like a burst of colorful magic in every pump!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNatural and allergen-free\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh pear scent\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDoes not irritate or dry skin\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shower gel on damp skin with light circular movements, rinse and dry.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Coco-Glucoside, Ipomoea Batatas (Potato) Root Extract, Cetyl Alcohol, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid, Aroma, Acacia Senegal Gum, Maltodextrin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51111034487111,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-natural-kids-shower-foam-150ml-609563.png?v=1740891412"},{"product_id":"luuv-sensitive-intimate-wash-140ml","title":"LUUV Sensitive Intimate Wash 140ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eSensitive Intimate Wash – the gentlest way to care for your most delicate areas! LUUV understands the importance of maintaining the fragile pH balance, and that’s why we’ve carefully selected herbal detergents that won’t disrupt it. With a perfectly balanced pH level of 3.5-4.5, you can trust that your intimate area will stay harmonious and healthy. Intimate wash is also completely odorless, so you can feel confident and comfortable all day long. Plus, it’s specially formulated for sensitive skin, so you can finally say goodbye to worries about irritation or redness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSensitive Intimate Wash is certified with the leading ECOCERT\/COSMOS eco-certificate. It’s time to indulge in the forbidden fruits of paradise – the secret to feeling fresh, confident, and beautifully balanced. Make the switch today, and rediscover the joy of taking care of yourself.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOdourless\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor sensitive skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith dense silky foam – also suitable for shaving\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCoco-Glucoside\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis a detergent, 100% natural (derived from coconut), environmentally friendly and certified. The detergent is gentle – also suitable for sensitive skin and children.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e100% natural\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ewheat protein\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003esoothes skin irritations and has an anti-inflammatory effect.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003eThe \u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eglycerin\u003c\/span\u003e we use is 100% natural and does not contain palm oil. The best feature of glycerin is that it takes moisture from the air and carries it into the skin, being able to carry it quite deeply. With a very strong moisturizing effect, and does not create a heavy\/oily feeling.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified | paraben free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eSuitable for intimate parts or for the whole body.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Starch, Coco-Glucoside, Glycerin, Glyceryl Oleate, Betaine, Cocos Nucifera, Cetyl alcohol, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Citric Acid, Xanthan gum, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115555979591,"sku":null,"price":8.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-sensitive-intimate-wash-140ml-859869.png?v=1740560026"},{"product_id":"petit-joliehair-body-shampoo-200ml","title":"Petit\u0026Jolie Hair \u0026 Body Shampoo 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetit\u0026amp;Jolie Hair\u0026amp;Body Shampoo cleanses and cares for the skin and hair in a mild way. The special composition ensures supple skin and prevents dehydration. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe shampoo is suitable for children with dry and sensitive skin. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt doesn't sting the eyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLike all our products, the baby hair \u0026amp; body shampoo does not contain parabens, SLS, paraffin or synthetic fragrances and dyes. The baby shampoo is made from 100% natural ingredients.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe bottle is made from 100% recycled plastic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eWhile taking a shower or bath, add a small amount of shampoo to your hand or washcloth and lightly massage the skin and hair of your baby. Rinse well with water afterwards.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Glycerin, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate, Coco-Glucoside, Decyl Glucoside, Xanthan Gum, Glyceryl Oleate, Parfum*, Dicaprylyl Ether, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Levulinate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Petit \u0026 Jolie","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51133856514375,"sku":null,"price":8.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/petitjolie-hair-body-shampoo-200ml-339984.png?v=1740808671"},{"product_id":"magrada-silky-body-cleanser-x-lauren-200ml","title":"Magrada Silky Body Cleanser X Lauren 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInfused with a hint of sparkle, this hydrating formula gently cleanses and nourishes your skin, leaving it soft and radiant with every use. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply gently on wet skin, then rinse off with water.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Coco-Glucoside, Glycolipids, Glycerin, Betaine, Xanthan Gum, Cucumis Sativus (Cucumber) Extract, Parfum, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Calcium Sodium Borosilicate, CI 77891, Tin Oxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 97,50%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52018922619207,"sku":null,"price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-silky-body-cleanser-x-lauren-200ml-3983999.jpg?v=1753801435"},{"product_id":"bee-it-regenerating-shower-gel-50ml","title":"BEE IT Regenerating Shower Gel 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSensory body wash with naturally active biological ingredients with a regenerating action.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003ePromotes the natural feeling of well-being thanks to the beneficial properties of propolis and organic honey.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eApply all over the body. Rinse off, appreciating your moment.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eAqua [Water], Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Parfum [Fragrance], Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Potassium sorbate, Sodium benzoate, Citric acid, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Coumarin, Limonene, Alpha-isomethyl ionone, Hydroxycitronellal, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel\/Honey*, Propolis wax.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e100% Natural Ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138338058567,"sku":null,"price":4.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-regenerating-shower-gel-250ml-523322.jpg?v=1739897335"},{"product_id":"bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-pink-for-kids-50ml","title":"BEE IT Shampoo \u0026 Body Wash Pink for Kids 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003ePhysiological pH shampoo \u0026amp; body wash rich in natural ingredients to enjoy the bath time as a pleasant experience of play and creativity. With organic aloe vera, sweet almond oil, organic honey and propolis, for a delicate and nourishing action.\u003cbr\u003eAmused and clean, his hair will be velvety and luminous, and his skin will be even softer and more fragrant.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Apply to hair and body and massage gently, then rinse.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Magnesium lauryl sulfate, Cocamidopropyl betaine, Coco-glucoside, Glyceryl oleate, Guar hydroxypropyltrimonium chloride, Glycerin, Aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, Parfum, Sodium benzoate, Potassium sorbate, Sodium chloride, Benzyl alcohol, Myristyl lactate, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Citric acid, Calendula officinalis extract, Dehydroacetic acid, Mel*, Propolis, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eNatural product with physiological pH 4.5-5.5\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52138376954183,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-pink-for-kids-250ml-813819.png?v=1739897342"},{"product_id":"bee-it-shampoo-body-wa