less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52143676195143,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-shampoo-body-wash-for-kids-maya-50ml-4970425.png?v=1756222789"},{"product_id":"hoia-natural-shower-gel-lavender-200ml","title":"HOIA Natural Shower Gel Lavender 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith HOIA Shower Gel, turn your shower ritual into a relaxing and calming aromatherapy session! This natural shower gel contains organic lavender and Saaremaa camelina oils, which gently cleanse and nourish your skin, leaving it wonderfully moisturized and pleasantly fragrant after washing. Suitable for daily use by both men and women, the lavender essential oil provides stress-relieving and calming effects.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is free from sulfates, silicones, and synthetic fragrances. Our shower gel has a gel-like texture, meaning it lasts longer.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the shower gel to damp skin, rub gently, enjoy the aromatherapy, and rinse.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Lauryl Glucoside, Disodium Laureth Sulfosuccinate, *Glycerin, Olive Oil Glycereth-8 esters, Betaine, Sodium Levulinate, *Lavandula Angustifolia Herb Oil, *Camelina Sativa seed oil, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, *Furcellaria Lumbricalis Extract, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Gluconate, Xanthan Gum, Lactic Acid, **Linalool, **Limonene, **Citral, **Geraniol.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Natural components of essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52247179034951,"sku":null,"price":15.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-natural-shower-gel-lavender-200ml-1455670.png?v=1756718907"},{"product_id":"hoia-natural-shower-gel-200ml","title":"HOIA Natural Shower Gel 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHOIA Shower Gel turns your washing ritual into an exciting experience! The natural shower gel gently cleanses and cares for your skin and leaves it pleasantly moisturized after washing. Shower gel has a fresh aroma and is suitable for everyday use by both men and women.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe essential oils contained in it have a refreshing, cleansing and mood-boosting effect. The product does not contain SLS, silicones or synthetic fragrances. HOIA Shower gel has a thicker gel composition, which means it lasts longer.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cb\u003e \u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan\u003eApply the shower gel to your skin, enjoy the aromas and rinse off with water. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Lauryl Glucoside, Disodium Laureth Sulfosuccinate, *Glycerin, Olive Oil Glycereth-8 esters, Betaine, Sodium Levulinate, *Citrus Aurantifolia Oil, *Cymbopogon Citratus Leaf Oil, *Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Oil,*Camelina Sativa seed oil, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, *Furcellaria Lumbricalis Extract, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Gluconate, Xanthan Gum, Lactic Acid, **Linalool, **Limonene, **Citral, **Geraniol.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Natural components of essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52247186047303,"sku":null,"price":15.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-natural-shower-gel-200ml-3790215.png?v=1756718905"},{"product_id":"nurme-spicy-orange-energising-body-wash-250ml","title":"NURME Spicy Orange Energising Body Wash 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTurns your washing ritual into a refreshing and energizing experience, leaving your body silky soft and smooth, and charmingly scented. Spicy Orange Energising Body Wash refreshes and cleanses your body, leaving it pleasantly moisturized. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetitgrain is a refreshing scent that keeps your mind and body alert. Sweet orange fills your bathroom and mind with wonderful aromas, leaving your body smelling irresistibly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply on skin and rub, then rinse with water.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Sodium Coco-Sulfate*, Coco-Glucoside*, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein*, Glyceryl Oleate*, Sodium Benzoate*, Potassium Sorbate*, Citric Acid, Sodium Chloride, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis Peel Oil, Litsea Cubeba Fruit Oil, Citrus Aurantium Amara Leaf Oil, Citral**, Linalool**, Geraniol**, Limonene**.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* Natural cosmetics approved ingredient\u003cbr\u003e** Occurs naturally in essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52690078236999,"sku":null,"price":8.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-spicy-orange-energising-body-wash-250ml-7508692.webp?v=1762389117"},{"product_id":"magrada-ph-balancing-intime-wash-100ml","title":"Magrada pH-Balancing Intime Wash 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis fragrance-free gentle intime wash provides you with the perfect balance of cleanliness, freshness and softness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGynaecologically and dermatologically tested.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply to damp skin, rinse thoroughly with warm water.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Sodium Laureth-5 Carboxylate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, PEG-200 Hydrogenated Glyceryl Palmate, Sodium Chloride, PEG-7 Glyceryl Cocoate, Polyquaternium-7, Coco-Glucoside, Jasminum Officinale (Jasmine) Flower Extract, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Extract, Lactic Acid, Panthenol, Chamomilla Recutita (Matricaria) Extract, Alcohol, Citric Acid, Glycerin, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 95,44%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e vegan \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e EU allergen-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52919534813511,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-ph-balancing-intime-wash-100ml-8159402.png?v=1765327449"}],"url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/kehapesu.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}